data.description: Awesome 3/2/2 in Windstone on a oversized corner lot!! This home isn't the normal home the owners built it and then did tons of upgrades like plantation shutters on the front, gas ran to the cooktop, custom trim, custom porch, new privacy fence with concrete curbing, extra parking the front, above ground pool, storage building, new roof.  Also the Layout is awesome with huge rooms, big open kitchen to the living room. This Home is NICE!!
